Title: Payment module
Description: Payment module is to allow the GSC staff to make payment for the customers.

Title: Reservation
Description: Reservation module is a module that allow GSC staff to reserve the seat for the customer.

Title: Registration
Description: Registration module is module that allow user which is GSC staff to login and help customer to register as member.

Title: As a GSC manager, i want to allow staff to login into the system, so that we can prevent unauthorized user to login
Description: To implement login function to the system.

Title: As a GSC company staff, i want to have member registration function for the system, so that i can help customer register as member easily.
As a GSC manager, i want the system to allow the staff to cancel the reservation so that customer can cancel the reservation if they suddenly want to cancel the reservation.
Description: To allow staff to cancel the reservation.

Title: As a GSC manager, i want the system to display the movie name and duration, so that the staff can select the movie that customer wants.
Description: To display movie name and duration

Title: As a GSC company manager, i want to have hall seat reserve function for the system,  so that staff do not need to take note which seat already reserved.
As GSC company staff, i want to print the ticket automatically by using the system, so that the i do not have to print ticket manually.
As a GSC company staff, i want to have calculation function for the system, so that i do not need to calculate the price manually.
As a GSC company manager, I want to view the staff system login history, so that i can check the staff working days.
Description: To check the login history of the staff

Title: As a GSC company staff, I want to have forget password function for the system, so that i can find back the password if i forgotten.
As a GSC company staff, I want to have change password function, so that i can change the password to the password that i can memories it easily.
